reviewText: This Spider-Man 2.1 shouldn't be that much money. The reason it's called 2.1 because it includes interviews with most of the actors/actresses. Also it provides commentary as the movie plays, so basically you watch the movie while a women talks about the scene. One last thing before I finish this review is that I bought this movie once at my local Kroger thinking it was a childhood movie I had skipped over, sooooo.....
